Short Description: Wheeled extinguishers are designed for tackling large fires.  Their huge capacity ensures a longer discharge time and higher rate of discharge than standard portable fire extinguishers, whilst the high quality trolley frames make the units easy to handle and enable fast deployment. AFF Foam trolley units are designed to cope with large Class A and Class B fires - for example fuel stations, large warehouses and manufacturing plants.  Despite their size they are desgned to be quickly moved and easily operated with one person.

Their huge capacity ensures a longer discharge time and higher rate of discharge than standard portable fire extinguishers, whilst the high quality trolley frames make the units easy to handle and enable fast deployment. Powder trolley units are tremendously effective, and their unsurpassed knock-down ability combined with the large capacity makes them suited for multi-class fire risks, for example large fuel stations, large manufacturing plants and heavy industry.  They are robust and designed for a long service life.
